    ITZ  Italy, EC.
    CAZ  Canada.
    DEZ  Germany, EC.
    USZ  United States of America.
    PKZ  Pakistan, Asia.
    FRZ  France, EC.
    NGZ  Nigeria, Africa.
</CN>
