<HEADLINE>
FT  30 DEC 93 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Overheated gold shares cooled off for the second day, but industrials
continued their upward march, particularly in the food sector.
The gold index lost 31 to 2,126, industrials gained 33 to 5,520 and the
overall index put on 2 to 4,799.
