<TEXT>
Lloyds Chemists has paid Pounds 1.1m cash for Trident Pharmaceuticals, a
wholesaler operating in the south of England and South Wales.
For the year to December 31 1992 Trident achieved turnover of Pounds 8.8m.
Tangible assets acquired amount to about Pounds 800,000.
